### `downloadstream`

Stream or download info. Quota cost is 1 units.

**ç«¯ç‚¹**: `GET /dl`


**å‚æ•°**:

- `id` (string) *å¿…éœ€*: Youtube Video Id or Shorts Id.

- `cgeo` (string) *å¿…éœ€*: Country code in ISO 3166 format of the end user. Not providing cgeo param may cost +1 quota. It is important to provide geo of the end user to get the best speed and direct links. If links are used in the server, then cgeo will be the geo of the server. Not providing cgeo param may lead to 403 issue

- `lang` (string): Language code for audio results based on availability. Like en, ru, hi, etc



---


